data.title: What professional guitarists use Gibson Les Pauls?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 14): What artist use Les Paul’s ONLY…I can’t think of any of the top of my head. There’s artists that are associated with the Les Paul Model. Now, if we quibble, someone like, say Slash…He actually used a ’59 burst Les Paul REPLICA.
